channel.title: How to open .cfg files?
channel.description: I was trying to test Allstar-Scape2 and I was changing name for the Fremennik Blade to Vesta Longsword and I don't have the Java icon on my Item folder, it shows up as a Microsoft Office Outlook Confguration File. WHAT DO I DO?!?! :(

item.title: How to open .cfg files?
item.dc:creator: @illslayu illslayu
item.description:
@illslayu wrote:

2x click the .cfg file then choose “find a program from a list” (or something like that) then choose “notepad” (recomended) and then go get someone (with RSPS editing skills(includes me)) to do the rest for you (also recomended) hope the non-insane stuff helped
